features: 【USB 3.2】This faster read speed USB 3.2 version of Tesla sentry mode USB flash drive has transfer rate of up to 200M/S. Adopting the USB3.2 Gen 1 specification, it can quickly read high-definition videos, large amounts of images, and other massive data files. It is backward compatible with USB3.0 and USB2.0 interfaces, improving efficiency and saving time.

【Precision manufacturing】The entire body of this Tesla USB drive is made of zinc alloy precision made, which not only has a textured appearance but also is sturdy and durable, wear-resistant and rust resistant, shockproof and drop resistant, with good heat dissipation, effectively protecting the chip.

【360° Rotation Protection】The unique design of the cover on the USB drive allows for 360 degree rotation, protecting the USB drive interface while effectively preventing the cover from being lost. The all-around rotation design provides more fun. Keyring hanging hole design for easy carrying.

【Plug and Play】This tesla usb flash drive is widely compatible with multiple devices, with downward compatibility with USB3.0/2.0 interfaces. Such as laptops, desktops, car systems, mobile phones, televisions, speakers etc. Whether driving or parked, the usb drive enables both Dashcam and Sentry Mode so you will be recording everything around your Tesla at all times.

【Super Stability】Built in high quality industrial-grade chip, After multiple tests, possessing strong repetitive reading and writing abilities, 130MB/s write speed, 230MB/s read speed. Selected materials and precision manufacturing ensure the service life and quality of the USB flash drive, ensuring stable performance.
